一木走過田中央。
疏疏魚骨，密密魚鱗，早晨開口，夜裡吃人。
山水畫山有水，水無聲，花常在，鳥不驚。

Items.mt:
Hee hee, I didn't expect you to find them all, this is the last puzzle! When you solve it, I will appear in front of you. <<
>>A log walks through the middle of the field. <<
>>The fish bones are sparse, the fish scales are dense, the mouth opens in the morning, and eats people at night. <<
>>The mountain has water, the water is silent, the flowers are always there, and the birds are not surprised. <<
>>Give a small inscription, there are five yo in total.
